cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human body analysis from images. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes deep generative models for the task. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with disentangling pose and appearance, which is a common problem in AI research. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating images of human bodies. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing and generating images of human bodies.
